Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能碰  手指会被卷进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此时妮诺扔掉的是橡胶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴里大爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此时妮诺喝的是碳酸饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个算式好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.07,0:23:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此时妮诺看到的是车牌号码
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  第11桥
